            <title>[LU-19159] Handle ip2nets yaml in jt_import</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19159</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Only a subset of jt_import&apos;s (lnetctl import command) was ported to the netlink APIs. One of the things that is missing is handling ip2nets configuration. This ticket tracks adding that capability.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
